ank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="560" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/11/597bdaa8-25af-4e3c-9c0c-a23f5ee8a9ab.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="双边交叉自喷水 + 适应多种立面：科沃斯 W1S 擦窗机器人 974 元国补新低" width="560" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">京东</span><span class="card-name">科沃斯 W1S 擦窗机器人</span></span><span class="card-abstract"> WG819-14</span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 多重优惠 974 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p>2024 年 11.11 大促全网好价合集：<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fcontentlist%3Fapi%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fnapi.ithome.com%252Fapi%252Ftopmenu%252Fgetmenufeeds%252F166%252F0%252Fnone%252F0%26title%3D2024%25E5%258F%258C11%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BF%2583%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E9%2580%2589%26mode%3D0" target="_blank" title="点此查看">点此查看</a></p><p><span class="font-color-red"><strong>京东无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 11111 元：<a href="https://u.jd.com/CaQySbH" target="_blank" title="点此抽今日红包"><strong>点此抽今日红包</strong></a></p><p><span class="font-color-orangered"><strong>天猫无门槛红包&nbsp;</strong></span>至高 24888 元：<strong><a href="https://s.click.taobao.com/w26hFPt" target="_blank">点此抽今日红包</a></strong></p><br /><p><br /></p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p><div class="tagging1">【广告】</div>
